{"tid":1174023,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[長長地嘅文 慎入]女朋友個肚","createTime":"2019-05-27T13:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T20:51:37.000Z","uid":24272,"like":5,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a4b830ec7991ff8ab5c5eb02f1d10d3d31c320","tid":1174023,"uid":24272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"望住女朋友個肚一日一日咁扁落去, 真係好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前喺香港痴住佢就可以同佢一齊, 逼下佢食嘢咁, 自從我一返咗去UK讀書就成日話唔食嘢, 又話咩懶得煮, 屋企人買埋返嚟又喺度扭話唔食, 講極都係唔肯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家講咗我諗個幾鐘先肯走去開包餅食, 食一兩塊又話唔想食, 再係咁落去真係會走火入魔, 會變成嗰種女人眼中嘅瘦,標準身型, 即係男人眼中嘅非洲飢民, 得棚骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢本身已經唔係嗰種有肉地嘅人, 而家仲要咁樣唔食嘢, 仲要成日話佢學校啲非洲飢民嘅女同學身材好正, 我真係好驚佢會變成嗰種身型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd00fa4e566e9cee8c89310e8cba8b3a891bc3c3","tid":1174023,"uid":5572,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"802d7ca452d6c37c524ecaee3a2f5913b099ce7d","tid":1174023,"uid":58685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"934de29dc0e288021ac68d51e98b7f70d0889e22","tid":1174023,"uid":24272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:52:56.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"df63d0e7f55ab249